    "desc": "One Heart One Soul bringing the power of arts and conversation to youth in drop-in centers, transitional homes and shelter for homelessness. Together we build platforms of impact and change.",
    "navbar": "Home\nWho We Are\nPrograms\nResources\nNews\nExhibits\nDonate",
    "text": "Social Enterprise Launching in Partnership with award-winning Monarch Thrift Shop\nHome\nWho We Are\nPrograms\nResources\nNews\nExhibits\nDonate\nWho We Are\nOne Heart One Soul brings the power of arts and conversation to youth in drop-in centers, transitional homes and shelter for homelessness.\nLEARN MORE\nOur Stories\n\"With a combined 15 years of impactful experience, Fouche said the social enterprise partnership will provide employment training, nationally recognized certificates, tangible resources and vast opportunities to help youth through their season of hardship and hopefully end the cycle of youth homelessness.\"- Invisible People\nREAD MORE\nOur Story\nWe invite you into this beautiful journey with us.\nRead More >\nGet Support\nPublic benefits, job placement, housing assistance, counseling, and more.\nRead More >\nGet Involved\nFind out how you can make an impact through volunteering with our workshops or clothing drive.\nRead More >\nGive\nFund critical\nCOVID-19 support and youth homeless 2021 work.\nRead More >\nPartner us\nFind out how your organization can make a difference by partnering with our organization.\nRead More >\n© 2021 One Heart One Soul \nConnect@1Heart1Soul.org\n  Mailing Address:\nOne Heart One Soul\n2875 N. Milwaukee Avenue\nChicago, IL 60614\nDonate\nJoin One Heart One Soul!\nJoin",
